## JSONObject type

`JSONObject` represents a JSON object, but unlike regular JSON, it has time tickets created by a logical clock to resolve conflicts.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export declare type JSONObject<T extends Indexable> = {
    getID?(): TimeTicket;
    toJSON?(): string;
} & T;
```
